trans-unit.source: Represents a reference to a data type.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en referanse til en datatype.

trans-unit.source: CodeTypeReferenceExpression can be used to reference a particular data type.
trans-unit.target: CodeTypeReferenceExpression kan brukes til å referere til en bestemt datatype.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression.Type%2A> property specifies the data type to reference.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"></xref> class using the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that indicates the data type to reference.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som angir datatypen for å referere til.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"></xref> class using the specified data type name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse med navnet på angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: The name of the data type to reference.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på datatypen å referere til.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"></xref> class using the specified data type.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av angitt datatype.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the data type to reference.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av typen å referere til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the data type to reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir datatypen for å referere til.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that indicates the data type to reference.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som angir datatypen for å referere til.
